<h1>About {{ site.name }}</h1>
<p>{{ site.name }} is a small collection of free calculators for electronics and embedded systems work: Ohm's law, resistor color codes, voltage dividers, LED resistors, and RC time constants.</p>
<p>Every calculator runs entirely in your browser. Nothing you type is sent to a server.</p>
<p>Found a bug or want a calculator added? Suggestions are welcome.</p>
